spell.name: Living Bomb
spell.description:
The target becomes a Living Bomb, taking 7,060 Fire damage over 3.9 sec, and then exploding to deal an additional 5,645 Fire damage to the target and all other enemies within 10 yards.



Other enemies hit by this explosion also become a Living Bomb, but this effect cannot spread further.
